        &hy HYPR ESC  &kp A         &kp S         &kp D         &kp F         &kp G         &none                             &kp LCTRL     &kp LALT           &kp LGUI      &kp RCTRL                        &none         &kp H         &kp J         &kp K         &kp L         &kp SEMI      &kp SQT
